<i>- ♪ I heard a newborn baby cry ♪</i>

34:35.682 --> 34:39.359
<i>♪ Through the night ♪</i>

34:45.525 --> 34:49.661
<i>♪ I heard a perfect echo die ♪</i>

34:53.491 --> 34:59.295
<i>♪ Into an anonymous wall
