35:02.083 --> 35:07.999
<i>♪ Somewhere deep inside ♪</i>

35:08.023 --> 35:13.963
<i>♪ Of my soul ♪</i>

35:18.024 --> 35:24.279
<i>♪ A natural beauty
should be preserved ♪</i>

35:24.355 --> 35:29.325
