too harsh ♪</i>

35:36.960 --> 35:39.627
What are you all looking at?
- John? John!

35:39.704 --> 35:41.129
John!

35:41.206 --> 35:44.015
<i>- ♪ Or someday you might
find your soul ♪</i>

35:44.092 --> 35:45.967
- Bernard.

35:46.044 --> 35:49.521
- John.
John, John...

35:49.598 --> 35:51.848
Can we get these people
out of the way, please?

35:51.925 --> 35:53.349
It's all right, John.

35:53.426 --> 35:55.404
It's all right, John.
I'm here now.

35:55.428 --> 35:57.257
<i>- ♪ Preserved ♪</i>

35:57.281 --> 36:01.900
<i>♪ Like a monument ♪</i>

36:01.976 --> 36:06.404
<i>♪ To nature ♪</i>

36:10.068 --> 36:12.535
- I wasn't expecting you.

36:12.612 --> 36:15.663
- I need you to do
something for me.

36:15.740 --> 36:17.040
- What?

36:17.116 --> 36:20.029
- Be the same.

36:27.043 --> 36:31.179
- You be the same
as you were before.

36:31.256 --> 36:34.182
I'll be the same.

36:34.259 --> 36:36.935
We're same.
Do you understand?

36:48.957 --> 36:51.750
- I wanna see my mom.

37:01.286 --> 37:05.296
<i>- What you saw
in that theater was fear.</i>

37:05.373 --> 37:08.299
<i>It defined them, the Savages.</i>

37:08.376 --> 37:11.177
<i>Their actions, customs,
traditions,</i>

37:11.254 --> 37:15.265
<i>obsessions, inventions.</i>

37:15.341 --> 37:17.776
<i>Fear was their undoing.</i>

37:21.514 --> 37:23.657
He trusts you?

37:25.393 --> 37:28.444
- I'm the only person
he knows here.

37:28.521 --> 37:29.865
- We're being tested, Counselor.

37:29.889 --> 37:32.282
That's what this is.
- Tested?

37:32.358 --> 37:36.327
- The system applies
strain to itself.

37:36.404 --> 37:38.632
Indra introduces
a destabilizing element

37:38.656 --> 37:41.749
to make itself stronger,
more stable.

37:41.826 --> 37:43.435
- John?

37:43.511 --> 37:46.170
- He needs someone like you...
to guide him.

37:46.247 --> 37:48.131
To bring him
into the social body.

37:48.207 --> 37:49.516
- Wh... How do...

37:49.592 --> 37:52.635
So you... you... you...
You want me to condition him?

37:52.712 --> 37:55.063
- He's not the one being tested.

38:01.387 --> 38:03.313
Your Director's dead.

38:03.389 --> 38:07.150
- Dead?
How?

38:07.226 --> 38:09.319
- He fell.

38:12.273 --> 38:14.073
- No, he didn't, did he?

38:15.918 --> 38:18.828
- I've seen it before.
- Yes, you have, haven't you?

38:21.074 --> 38:24.092
- Wha... what... what is happening?

38:25.745 --> 38:28.338
- We're at the beginning
of something, Counselor,

38:28.414 --> 38:31.174
something necessary.

38:31.250 --> 38:33.134
This is our test.

38:33.211 --> 38:35.219
We will pass.

38:37.423 --> 38:40.169
- And you've just
become important.

39:30.735 --> 39:34.529
- I don't want you
to feel like this, John.

39:34.605 --> 39:37.268
I'm gonna help you.

